{
  "stem": "23350.6",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it helped me a lot to know it sometime in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It really helped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at the time when I learned corsetry-- because I learned corsetry, I had to come to live in London.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is how I came to live in a hostel in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the girls in [INAUDIBLE] who lived there were from before the war they came.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was the only girl who actually came from after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was one girl who got-- particularly got very friendly with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was from Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she talked me in one day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wanted very much I should go with her to Hyde Park.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hyde Park?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've never heard of Hyde Park.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't even know it at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she told me, there's going to-- there are going to be speakers from Israel, and we should go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She drove me so much about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She told me in the morning, Minia, let's wash our hair.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Come on, let's dress up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But in those days, I was already learning corsetry, and I was being paid by my employer, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he always tried to give me a little bit of extra, so that I shouldn't be so terribly short.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So and clothes was very cheap, so I managed to get myself a cloth-- something to wear here and there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So, sure enough, I had something to wear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, we changed around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She had something which she liked-- she, she-- very nice outfit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But she wore it so often, she was already fed up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She said, Minia, can I change with you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was wearing hers, and she was wearing mine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "What was her name?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
